    <!-- code a "How it works" section -->

<div class="container root-container">
  <h2 class="">Our offer</h2>
  <div class="row">
      <div class="card col root-card ">
        <%# <img src="https://lewagon.github.io/landing-page-challenge/images/apply.svg"> %>
        <div class="root-card-content">
          <h3>Rent-out your books</h3>
          <p>You have books ? Rent-them to our community members. Unlock the magic of reading by sharing your collection with our vibrant community! Have a treasure trove of books? Let your literary gems find new homes by renting them out to fellow members. Join us in creating a shared world of knowledge and stories – because great books deserve to be passed on!</p>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="card col root-card">
        <%# <img src="https://lewagon.github.io/landing-page-challenge/images/learn.svg"> %>
        <div class="root-card-content">
          <h3>Borrow books</h3>
          <p>You would like to read books? Borrow them from our community members. Dive into a world of endless possibilities by borrowing captivating books from our generous community members! If you have a thirst for knowledge or a craving for thrilling stories, look no further. Join our community, where book lovers come together to share the joy of reading. Borrowing has never been more exciting – let the adventure begin!</p>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
